Ed says he can't get through to Digi Controls. Tried for 2 weeks? I got through first try. Can't do the job without the whole car. I spoke with John D. He recommended Mass Electronics. I called. They can supply a replacement radio for $1400.
Meanwhile, I spoke with customer who said the problem has been there since he picked up the vehicle. (See call record)
Shop is saying they have been trying to make this claim since November 2018, our first recorded contact is Feb 26, 2019.
Customer claims Progressive has be trying to repair since August 2018. Tim M and John D involved.
Seems like this is a pre-existing problem. Standby for more.
